{"ID":"20230724015052-1twuiqv","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"icon":"1f3f9","id":"20230724015052-1twuiqv","tags":"Docker,需要仔细看,未完成","title":"10. 持久化存储和卷间状态共享","updated":"20230724015119"},"Children":[{"ID":"20230724015055-4ulb9jy","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20230724015055-4ulb9jy","updated":"20230724015055"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1. 存储卷的简介"}]},{"ID":"20230724015055-zgjb7vw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230724015055-zgjb7vw","updated":"20230724015055"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"一个主机或容器的目录树是由一组挂载点创建而成，这些挂载点描述了如何能构建出一个或多个文件系统 。存储卷是容器目录树上的挂载点，其中一部分主机目录树已经被挂载了。大多数人只熟悉一点点文件系统和挂载点，很少对其进行定制。比起任何其他的Docker话题，存储卷会更难一些。"}]},{"ID":"20230724015055-1z03sld","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20230724015055-1z03sld","updated":"20230724015055"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1. 存储卷提供容器无关的数据管理方式"}]},{"ID":"20230724015055-wj771lg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230724015055-wj771lg","updated":"20230724015055"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"数据示例根据其范围或者接入容器方式的不同，分成以下几种："}]},{"ID":"20230724015055-0q08wa5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230724015055-0q08wa5","updated":"20230724015055"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"■ 数据库软件与数据库中的数据"}]},{"ID":"20230724015055-f6xqelw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230724015055-f6xqelw","updated":"20230724015055"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"■ web应用程序与日志数据"}]},{"ID":"20230724015055-bqa0sc1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230724015055-bqa0sc1","updated":"20230724015055"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"■ web数据处理应用程序的输入和输出数据"}]},{"ID":"20230724015055-i387zpx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230724015055-i387zpx","updated":"20230724015055"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"■ web服务器与静态内容"}]},{"ID":"20230724015055-f0dao4g","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230724015055-f0dao4g","updated":"20230724015055"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"■ 产品与支持工具"}]},{"ID":"20230724015055-69wr45w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230724015055-69wr45w","updated":"20230724015055"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"存储卷可分离关注点，并为架构组件创建模块化。这种模块化设计帮助你更轻松地了解、构建、支持和重用大型系统的部件。"}]},{"ID":"20230724015055-cdg7oa4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230724015055-cdg7oa4","updated":"20230724015055"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"镜像适合打包和分发相对静态的文件，如程序；"}]},{"ID":"20230724015055-iic87t6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230724015055-iic87t6","updated":"20230724015055"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"存储卷则持有动态或专门数据。这种区别使得镜像可重用，数据也可以简单分享。"}]},{"ID":"20230724015055-g4qn74x","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230724015055-g4qn74x","updated":"20230724015055"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"这种相对静态和动态文件空间的分离，允许应用程序或镜像的作者，实现高级模式，例如多态和可组合工具。"}]},{"ID":"20230724015055-k3mrq01","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230724015055-k3mrq01","updated":"20230724015055"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"存储卷可以隔离应用程序和主机的关系。镜像被装载到主机，创建出一个容器。Docker 不知道主机在哪里运行，只能判断哪些文件在容器中可用。这意味着Docker本身就没有办法利用主机上的设施，如装载的网络存储，或混合光纤和固态硬盘。但有主机知识的用户可以使用存储卷，在容器中将这些目录映射到主机的存储上。"}]},{"ID":"20230724015055-katewml","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20230724015055-katewml","updated":"20230724015055"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2. NoSQL 数据库使用存储卷"}]},{"ID":"20230724015055-25mmos3","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20230724015055-25mmos3","updated":"20230724015055"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.存储卷的类型"}]},{"ID":"20230724015055-3iclfoj","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20230724015055-3iclfoj","updated":"20230724015055"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3. 共享存储卷"}]},{"ID":"20230724015055-476llnt","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20230724015055-476llnt","updated":"20230724015055"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"4. 存储卷的高级容器模式"}]},{"ID":"20230724015055-cy9ao4t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230724015055-cy9ao4t","updated":"20230724015055"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"在现实世界中，存储卷可用来实现多种文件系统的定制和容器的交互。"}]}]}